title: Tumi Voyageur Mila Small Sling 484701 - Overview
description:
Tumi Voyageur Mila Small Sling - 484701-BLACK
http://www.abt.com/product/96440/Tumi-484701BLACK.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=484701_20160419

From our stylish new Voyageur collection comes this chic smaller-sized sling. This versatile trend-right silhouette is fun to carry and ideal for days when a big bag is not needed. Deceptively small it offers a multitude of organizational pockets for your key essentials and even converts from a sling to a waistpack if you so desire.
Specifications:
• Construction Material: Nylon   
• Interior:
o Open slit pocket
o D-ring
• Exterior:
o Front and back pockets with magnetic closure
o Vertical front zip pocket
o 2 D-rings for sling to waistpack convertibility
o Adjustable webbing strap
o Leather trim
